Html:
I got this when processing an uploaded excel:

 

Uncaught exception 'Exception' with message 'Cell entry B2 no longer exists in MemCache'.

 

It says   ......./PHPExcel/CachedObjectStorage/Memcache.php on line 124
It means one of two things: either you've run out of memcache space, or that the cell data has been flushed from memcache (timeout, least recently accessed, whatever)
